articles.title: Willie Spence, 'American Idol' Season 19 runner-up, dead at 23 - CNN
articles.description: Willie Spence, a singer who as a teen went viral with his rendition of Rihanna's hit "Diamonds" and was the runner up on Season 19 on "American Idol, has died the show confirmed in a social media posting on Wednesday.

articles.title: Women With Cancer More Dissatisfied Than Men With Care Received - Medscape
articles.description: A new survey from the American Cancer Society finds that women patients are more dissatisfied than men with the medical care they have received.
